      "text": "teem dewis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Aroëra / kas pee tahs\nArnona Uppes Mallas irr/ un ta\nPilsfahta/kas Uppes Widdû irr/\nun wiſſu Klaijuma no Medbas\nlihds Dibonant.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſus Siona Pils-\nfahtus ta Amoritern Kehnixa/\nkas Eṣbonâ waldtja lihds tai Am-\nmona Behrnu Rohbeschai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Gileadu/ un to Gesuri-\ntern un to Maakatiteru Rohbe-\nschas / un wiſſu Ermona Kalnu/\nun wiſſu Bahsanu lihds Salkai.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſſu Kehnixa Walsti\nOga eekſç Bahsana/ kas Aṣtoro-\nta un Eedrejös waldija / tas bija\natlizzis no teem atliffuscheem\nMilseem / ko Mohsus irr apka-\nwig un iṣdsinnis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr Israëka Behrni\nne iṣdsinne tohs Gesuritens un\nMaakatitens / bet Gesurs un\nMaakats dshwoja Israëta Wid-\ndû lihds schodeen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tikkai tai Lewja Zilti ue\ndewe wiꞥſch eemantojamu Teefu/\ntee Uppuki ta KUNGA ta Isra-\netka Deewa irr winnas Jhpa-\nschums; ittin ka wiꞥſch tai run-\nnajs irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta dewe Mohsustai Ruh-\nbenza Behrnu Zilti / pehz ẜawahm\nSaimehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka winnu Rohbeschta bija\nno Aroëra/ kas pee tahs Arnona\nUppes Mallas irr / un tas Pils-\nfahts/ kas Uppes Widdû irr/ un\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eṣbons / un wiſſi wiṣṣa\nPilsfahti/ kas klaijâ Semmê irr\nDibons / un Bamot-Baële / un\nBet-Baal-Meons.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Jakza / un Kedemots\nun Mervaiz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Kiriatäina/ un Sib-\nma / un Zeret-Saïrs us to Ka-\nnu tahs Eelejas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Bet-Beers/un Asdod\nPiṣga/ un Bet-Jesimot.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſi Klaijuma Pils-\nfahti/ un wiſſu Kehnixan Walsts\nSiona ta Amoritern Kehnixa/ ka\nEṣbonâ waldija/ ko Mohsus apka-\nwe lihds ar teem Midijanas Lee-\nleem-Rungrem / Eru un Rekt-\nnu/ un Zuru/ un Uru / un Rebu-\nteem Siona Waldineekem / ka-\ntai Semmê dshwoja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta patt irr tee Israë-\nBehrni ar Sohbinu nokawufs-\nBileamu/ Beora Dehlu to Sit-\nletaju/lihds ar teem/ kas no win-\nneem nokauti irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu Rubbensa Behr-\nna Robbescha bija ta Jardana\nlihds ar (fawu) Rohbeschta. Schi-\nirr Rubbensa Behrnu Jhpaschunn-\npehz fawahm Satnehm / Pils-\nfahteen/ un winnu Zeemeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Gada Zilti / teem Ga-\nda Behrneem pehz fawahm Sa-\nmehm/ dewe Mohsus/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ka winnu Rohbeschta bij\nJaësers/ un wiſſi Gileadas Pils-\nfahti/ un weena Semmes Pu-\nto Ammona Behrnu / lihds Are-\neram/ kas preeffch Rabbas irr.\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
